{"tid":303641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18:15  警方開始拘捕在場人士，單人也拘捕","createTime":"2017-06-30T10:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T11:14:27.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e080b386cc4dcf2c319463046de68c28fdd97730","tid":303641,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"【警方威脅開始集會將展開拘捕行動】<br />\n由於尖沙咀鐘樓被警方及康文署嚴密封鎖，敝黨早前轉往鄰近尖東市政局百周年紀念公園架設講台，惟遭警方阻撓。<br />\n<br />\n警民關係科警員警告召集人陳浩天，如敝黨成員開始佈置場地，將會立即拘捕。現時大量警察正於該處抄身份證及搜身，請支持者避免在該處聚集。請保持留意敝黨Facebook專頁或telegram channel之最新消息。"},{"pid":"ef81526cf8e2f932ff6f521881a06aac601f48fa","tid":303641,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdad1b3ea6c9171e1ea39aa7d7a508c4e2213f44","tid":303641,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fd9f4d05aa368ab2586510a50a6fb8703d29c7b","tid":303641,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"突發"},{"pid":"253f81d16e61e246f670118a6b24e9c4e16678b7","tid":303641,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:39:45.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"495f6603f7d614917df0b1122d6650f865c1c5d1","tid":303641,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:43:31.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"9d0482a9a4fe10ba4a70aba9cd8bb0ed7cf6bce1","tid":303641,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ab1837eb060791e035530723d148070132fb04b","tid":303641,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:47:38.000Z","msg":",,,"},{"pid":"0522daa925e5b0ae69ce4b2a520d3f3ff993f796","tid":303641,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:52:45.000Z","msg":","},{"pid